OL,3,C#110 million plans revealed for '21st
OL,4,Ccentury leisure destination'
OL,6,FJersey's government has released plans
OL,7,Fworth #110 million to redevelop Fort
OL,8,FRegent into a "premier leisure and
OL,9,Fentertainment hub".
OL,11,FThe Jersey Development Company (JDC)
OL,12,Fhas developed proposals to refurbish
OL,13,Fthe venue and install several external
OL,14,Fand interior features, with a focus on
OL,15,Fchildren and families.
OL,17,FIt is not the first time the
OL,18,Fgovernment has offered to revive the
OL,19,Fsite, with previous politicians
OL,20,Fabandoning the last three plans
OL,21,Fpitched in the past decade.
