OL,6,FConstable Andy Jehan, Jersey's
OL,7,FInfrastructure Minister, remains
OL,8,Foptimistic that work to clear the site
OL,9,Fcan start in December of this year.
OL,11,FConstable Jehan explains: "We want
OL,12,Fpeople to think of Fort Regent as a
OL,13,Fnew, vibrant area where both locals
OL,14,Fand visitors can enjoy themselves
OL,15,Fthroughout the year, and I think
OL,16,Fthat's within our grasp.
OL,18,F"It will be quicker, it'll be safer,
OL,19,Fand it will also be cheaper for us to
OL,20,Fredevelop - we hope to open in the
OL,21,Ffourth quarter of 2028."
