OL,6,FThe JDC has published a series of
OL,7,Fillustrative pictures for the
OL,8,Famenities they are proposing for Fort
OL,9,FRegent.
OL,11,FThere are several key features listed,
OL,12,Fincluding:
OL,14,FA hotel is also included on the site
OL,15,Fof the former swimming pool, but it
OL,16,Fwill be privately funded.
OL,18,FLee Henry, the CEO at JDC, says they
OL,19,Fare excited about the development. The
OL,20,FJDC will also carefully consider how
OL,21,Fto preserve the Fort's heritage assets.
