OL,6,FMr Henry explains: "We've looked at
OL,7,Fthis from a refurbishment perspective,
OL,8,Fso we're looking at maintaining the
OL,9,Fprofile of the roof and all of the
OL,10,F'Listed' components of the Fort.
OL,12,F"We will refurbish them into - once
OL,13,Fagain - a fantastic, all-weather
OL,14,Famenity for the island community."
OL,16,FAn intrusive survey will also be
OL,17,Fcarried out to remove asbestos in the
OL,18,Froof when work hopes to start in early
OL,19,F2026.
