OL,6,FIt will be up to States Members to
OL,7,Fapprove the amount of funding that can
OL,8,Fbe invested in the annual budget
OL,9,Fdebate in Autumn.
OL,11,FFunding will come through the Fort's
OL,12,Frevenues, borrowing, existing
OL,13,Fallocation for capital budgets, and
OL,14,Fadditional government contributions.
OL,16,FConstable Jehan hopes to convince
OL,17,FMembers that investment is crucial for
OL,18,Fthe proposal's success.
