OL,6,FHe explains: "#110 million is
OL,7,Fsignificant capital, and we spent a
OL,8,Flot of time working on the revenue
OL,9,Fbecause it's vital we get enough money
OL,10,Fin from the facility to ensure we can
OL,11,Fmaintain it."
OL,13,FResidents are now invited to
OL,14,Fcontribute to an independent public
OL,15,Fsurvey opening today (Wednesday 2
OL,16,FApril).
OL,18,FThe JDC will also conduct
OL,19,Fpresentations and consultations with
OL,20,Fschools for the next two months to
OL,21,Festablish the views of under-18s.
