OL,6,FThe Infrastructure Minister clarified
OL,7,Fthat young people are "the customers"
OL,8,Fwho will most likely benefit from this
OL,9,Fscheme.
OL,11,FConstable Jehan adds: "People are
OL,12,Ftelling us all the time that they want
OL,13,Fsome more leisure facilities,
OL,14,Fparticularly for the youngsters.
OL,16,F"We are listening and want to be sure
OL,17,Fthat the regeneration meets the needs
OL,18,Fand ambitions of the public."
